creator: Happs News
descriptionHtml:
Happs brings you the most fascinating, important, interesting “happenings" in the world. LIVE.

A brand new concept of live news, Happs enables contributors to live stream from any location using their own mobile devices within minutes of a breaking event, but produces the published product in an engaging, polished format much like a network news channel.

Happs prides itself on having a vast network of journalists around the world and welcomes new contributors from every part of the globe. If you are an aspiring or professional video journalist and wish to be part of our network, please contact us!

If you are a Happs contributor, download this app to be able to stream any time, from anywhere. That is the power of the Network of Now.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• You can now post URLs, images, and text to Happs from other apps via our new sharing sheet
• Chat messages no longer fade out for broadcasters after taking in user feedback
• Bug fixes

• Earn money from your viewers through sponsorships and financial awards

title: Happs

creator: Happs News
descriptionHtml:
After months of hard work and listening to feedback from our community we're excited to unveil the next iteration of Happs. We've redesigned the entire app from the ground up introducing new features, best in class tools and a user experience designed to surface the most talented creators to the widest possible audience.

Home Feed

Discover featured posts from the top creators that our algorithm surfaces for you, get easy access to the people you're following and see their streams and discover new creators in our More from Happs feed designed to help you find content to escape with.

Awards

New 3D and interactive awards to help you show your appreciation and support to the creators, get noticed as we highlight the top supporters and award givers in each stream and give access to the creators to thank their loyal community.

Studio

A new and improved Vertical First studio, focusing on sharing your streams to other platforms in the optimum format, your favorite locations are here, Facebook Live, YouTube Live, Twitch Live, Twitter Live and more, with some special new additions coming soon!

Profile

Your profile is now your billboard, upload a custom channel trailer to immediately show your viewers who you are, its time to get your best clips and highlight them for the world.
